    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2530190435431792205.png",
                "id": "talent21489",
                "key": "Wind Spirit Creation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Wind Spirit Creation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>, target berganti ke Karakter sebelumnya secara paksa.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/dceff798de3e5575ac1c3dad5718d18e_3912753510845684753.png",
                "id": "talent60626",
                "key": "Astable Anemohypostasis Creation - 6308",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Astable Anemohypostasis Creation - 6308"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Large Wind Spirit</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/28de70f699de4ba7cf0f77f2fcfb1483_8307703107345555094.png",
                "id": "talent71896",
                "key": "Forbidden Creation - Isomer 75 / Type II",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Forbidden Creation - Isomer 75 / Type II"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai: </span>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah Karakter atau Panggilan-mu memicu reaksi Swirl:</span> Ubah Tipe Elemen kartu ini dah ubah DMG yang diakibatkannya ke Elemen yang tercampur dalam Swirl. (Hanya dapat digunakan sekali sebelum meninggalkan arena.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6739420436976408797.png",
                "id": "talent76208",
                "key": "Large Wind Spirit",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/b91de96bc6f45b8b9a5b10ab4a127a88_7783275260377931999.png",
                "title": "Large Wind Spirit"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/15/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_5255967829654960027.png",
                "id": "talent52017",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3879600572753419984.png",
